data.message: Fix Duro vector search - migration, embedding worker, and upsert logic: Fixed 3 bugs: (1) m001_add_vectors.py migration now properly checks for vector table existence separately from FTS, (2) embedding_worker.py now uses real FastEmbed embeddings instead of placeholder zeros, (3) index.py upsert_embedding uses DELETE+INSERT since vec0 doesn't support UPSERT. All 510 artifacts now embedded, hybrid search operational.
